---
title: Smart Provençal-Style Fish and Shrimp Stew with Zesty Garlic Aioli
description: This comforting stew, deeply flavoured with aromatics, sweetened with tomatoes and topped with shrimp, gets a zesty pick-me-up from tarragon and lemon. A dollop of garlicky aioli adds a hint of creaminess that makes this dinner unforgettable!
